Development Trends of TSL Clubs¶

In [2]:
df_tsl = df[df['Division'] == 'Turkish Super League']

df_tsl_clubs = df_tsl.groupby(['Club'])['Name'].count().to_frame().reset_index()
df_tsl_clubs = df_tsl_clubs[(df_tsl_clubs['Name'] > 1)]

clubs = df_tsl_clubs['Club']
df_tsl = df[df['Club'].isin(clubs)]

df_tsl_ca = df_tsl.groupby(['Club'])['CA'].nlargest(23).to_frame().reset_index()
df_tsl_ca = df_tsl_ca.groupby(['Club'])['CA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index().sort_values('Club')

df_tsl_pa = df_tsl.groupby(['Club'])['PA'].nlargest(23).to_frame().reset_index()
df_tsl_pa = df_tsl_pa.groupby(['Club'])['PA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index().sort_values('Club')

df_comp = df_tsl_ca
df_comp['PA'] = df_tsl_pa['PA']
df_comp['Dist'] = df_comp['PA'] - df_comp['CA'] # Distance between Potential and Current Ability
df_comp['Rate'] = 100 - (df_comp['CA'] / df_comp['PA'] * 100) # Rate of team's part that could potentially improve
df_comp = df_comp.sort_values('Rate', ascending = False)

plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = 24,8
df_comp.plot.bar(x = 'Club', y = ['Rate', 'Dist'])

top5leagues = ('Italian Serie A','Spanish First Division','Bundesliga','English Premier Division','Ligue 1 Conforama')
df = df[df['Division'].isin(top5leagues)]

goalkeepers = pd.DataFrame()
defenders = pd.DataFrame()
midfielders = pd.DataFrame()
attackers = pd.DataFrame()

attackers = attackers.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "AM (C)"])
attackers = attackers.append(df[df["Best Pos"] == "AM (L)"])
attackers = attackers.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "AM (R)"])
attackers = attackers.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "ST (C)"])
#display(attackers.sort_index())

goalkeepers = goalkeepers.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "GK"])
#display(goalkeepers.sort_index())

midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "M (C)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "M (L)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "M (R)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "AM (C)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "AM (L)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "AM (R)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "WB (L)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "WB (R)"])
midfielders = midfielders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "DM"])
#display(midfielders.sort_index())

defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "D (C)"])
defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "D (L)"])
defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "D (R)"])
defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "DM"])
defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "WB (L)"])
defenders = defenders.append(df[df['Best Pos'] == "WB (R)"])
#display(defenders.sort_index())

goalkeepers_largestca = goalkeepers.groupby(['Division','Club'])['CA'].nlargest(2)
goalkeepers_largestca = goalkeepers_largestca.to_frame()
goalkeepers_largestca = goalkeepers_largestca.reset_index()
goalkeepers_largestca_mean = goalkeepers_largestca.groupby(['Division'])['CA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index()
#display(goalkeepers_largestca_mean)

defenders_largestca = defenders.groupby(['Division','Club'])['CA'].nlargest(7)
defenders_largestca = defenders_largestca.to_frame()
defenders_largestca = defenders_largestca.reset_index()
defenders_largestca_mean = defenders_largestca.groupby(['Division'])['CA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index()
#display(defenders_largestca_mean)

midfielders_largestca = midfielders.groupby(['Division','Club'])['CA'].nlargest(10)
midfielders_largestca = midfielders_largestca.to_frame()
midfielders_largestca = midfielders_largestca.reset_index()
midfielders_largestca_mean = midfielders_largestca.groupby(['Division'])['CA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index()
#display(midfielders_largestca_mean)

attackers_largestca = attackers.groupby(['Division','Club'])['CA'].nlargest(5)
attackers_largestca = attackers_largestca.to_frame()
attackers_largestca = attackers_largestca.reset_index()
attackers_largestca_mean = attackers_largestca.groupby(['Division'])['CA'].mean().to_frame().reset_index()
#display(attackers_largestca_mean)

top5laegue_means = pd.DataFrame()
top5laegue_means['Division'] = attackers_largestca_mean['Division']
top5laegue_means['Attackers CA Mean'] = attackers_largestca_mean['CA']
top5laegue_means['Midfielders CA Mean'] = midfielders_largestca_mean['CA']
top5laegue_means['Defenders CA Mean'] = defenders_largestca_mean['CA']
top5laegue_means['Goalkeepers CA Mean'] = goalkeepers_largestca_mean['CA']
top5laegue_means.index = top5laegue_means['Division'] 
del top5laegue_means['Division']
display(top5laegue_means)

def funct1(a,b):
    a = pd.DataFrame().assign(Height = a['Height'], Weight = a['Weight'], Age = a['Age'], Value = a['Value'], CA = a['CA'], PA = a['PA'])
    matrix = a.corr()
    f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(15,15))
    sns.heatmap(matrix,square=True,cmap=b, annot = True)

Boxplots and Swarmplots of top 5 leagues¶

In [28]:
ita = df.groupby(['Division']).get_group('Italian Serie A')
spa = df.groupby(['Division']).get_group('Spanish First Division')
ger = df.groupby(['Division']).get_group('Bundesliga')
eng = df.groupby(['Division']).get_group('English Premier Division')
fra = df.groupby(['Division']).get_group('Ligue 1 Conforama')

def valuefunct(a):
    a_count = a.groupby(['Club'])['Name'].count().to_frame().reset_index()
    a_count = a_count[(a_count['Name'] > 22)]
    list1 = a_count['Club']
    a = a[a['Club'].isin(list1)]
    b = a.groupby(['Club'])['Value'].nlargest(22)
    b = b.to_frame()
    b = b.reset_index()
    plt.figure(figsize=(30,6))
    sns.swarmplot(x="Club", y="Value", data=b).set_title("Takımların Oyuncu Piyasa Değerleri")
    sns.boxplot(x="Club", y ="Value", data =b, showfliers=False, showbox=False, showcaps=False,
            showmeans=True, meanline=True, meanprops={'color': 'k', 'ls': '-', 'lw': 4}, 
            medianprops={'visible': False}, whiskerprops={'visible': False});
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.show()
    
def cafunct(a):
    a_count = a.groupby(['Club'])['Name'].count().to_frame().reset_index()
    a_count = a_count[(a_count['Name'] > 22)]
    list1 = a_count['Club']
    a = a[a['Club'].isin(list1)]
    b = a.groupby(['Club'])['CA'].nlargest(22)
    b = b.to_frame()
    b = b.reset_index()
    plt.figure(figsize=(30,6))
    sns.swarmplot(x="Club", y="CA", data=b).set_title("Oyuncuların Yetenek Değerleri")
    sns.boxplot(x="Club", y ="CA", data =b, showfliers=False, showbox=False, showcaps=False,
            showmeans=True, meanline=True, meanprops={'color': 'k', 'ls': '-', 'lw': 4}, 
            medianprops={'visible': False}, whiskerprops={'visible': False});
    plt.xticks(rotation=90)
    plt.show()

tprint("ITALY")
valuefunct(ita)
cafunct(ita)
